l gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Inside your new repo, clic=
k <strong>Add file</strong> =E2=86=92 <strong>Upload files</strong></li>
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Drag and drop the <code cl=
ass=3D"bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 wh=
itespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">leviathan_os_v=
2.html</code> file I gave you</li>
